---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Navigation Lab | Palo"
	description="用于测试二级导航展开与当前项激活态的页面。"
>
	<main class="page">
		<nav class="crumbs" aria-label="面包屑">
			<a href="/studio">← Back to Studio</a>
		</nav>

		<header class="header">
			<p class="eyebrow">Level Two Test Page</p>
			<h1>Navigation Lab</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				如果你当前看到 Studio 父级菜单保持展开，并且当前子项高亮，说明二级菜单导航的核心逻辑已经跑通。
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card">
			<h2>Checklist</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>桌面端父级菜单是否可展开</li>
				<li>移动端菜单是否能正确显示当前子项</li>
				<li>点击空白处是否关闭菜单</li>
				<li>从子页返回父级是否顺畅</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		max-width: var(--page-max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem var(--page-gutter) 5rem;
	}

	.crumbs a {
		display: inline-block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--text-strong);
		font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
		padding: 0.35rem 0.55rem;
		border-radius: 0.55rem;
	}

	.crumbs a:hover {
		background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.06);
		color: var(--link);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 1rem 0 0.35rem;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.lead {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		padding: 1.25rem;
	}

	.card h2 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
</style>
